== 相關事件 ==
=== 網站被駭事件 ===
{{main|2010年廣州亞運電子襪判罰爭議}}
因[[2010年廣州亞運電子襪判罰爭議|2010年廣州亞運電子襪判罰爭議]]而在官方網站上發布標題為「Shocking Act of Deception by Chinese Taipei（中華台北－驚人的騙術）」的新聞稿<ref>{{cite news | language = en | author = 亞洲跆拳道聯盟 | url = http://en.mastaekwondo.com/2010/11/18/shocking-act-of-deception-by-chinese-taipei/ | title = Shocking Act of Deception by Chinese Taipei | date = 2010-11-18 | accessdate = 2011-01-06 | archive-date = 2011-01-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110101204241/http://en.mastaekwondo.com/2010/11/18/shocking-act-of-deception-by-chinese-taipei/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，令台灣人民群情激憤。官方網站在2010年11月19日遭駭客入侵<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | author =  | url = http://tech.ifeng.com/internet/detail_2010_11/19/3163540_0.shtml | title = “亞洲跆拳道聯盟”官網被台灣網友黑掉 | publisher = [[鳳凰網|鳳凰網]] | date = 2010-11-19 | accessdate = 2011-01-06 | archive-date = 2019-07-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190724030123/http://tech.ifeng.com/internet/detail_2010_11/19/3163540_0.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，甚至被迫臨時關閉網站。11月22日事發後，亞跆盟刻意採用[[防火牆_(计算机)|防火牆機制]]，將[[台灣|台灣]]與[[澳洲|澳洲]]的[[IP位址|IP位址]]全數封鎖<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | author = 湯蕙如 | url = http://www.nownews.com/2010/11/22/339-2666586.htm | title = 亞跆盟官網使賤招？　用防火牆封鎖台灣 IP 騙說遭駭！ | publisher = [[今日新聞網|今日新聞網]] | date = 2010-11-22 | accessdate = 2011-01-06 | archive-date = 2010-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101125152259/http://www.nownews.com/2010/11/22/339-2666586.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

